  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Essential Twin Rooms</strong> are 18m² and sleep two to three people, with a small third bed. </p>
<p><strong>Essential Twin rooms with View</strong> are 18m² and sleep two to three people. These rooms have a forest or mountain view.</p>
<p><strong>Essential Twin rooms with Mont Blanc Views</strong> are 18m² and sleep two to three people. These rooms have views of Mont Blanc.</p>
<p><strong>Single rooms</strong> are available with a supplement, please call to book.</p>
<p>Beds are made every day and daily housekeeping.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Bathtub and WC</li>
<li>Cots will fit in all rooms when occupied by two people and the baby.</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
